init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are the Queen of Bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I want you to go out and find the most beautiful flower you can find.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That's it, that's the one" you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Queen of Bees is a very powerful character, with the ability to control any bee in the area.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Your Majesty, we have located a patch of rare orchids, and we are bringing you their pollen"
